NAME

libEndpointSecurity —
Library used to interact with the Endpoint Security (ES) subsystem

DESCRIPTION

libEndpointSecurity exports interfaces allowing ES clients to interact with the ES subsystem, including operations like subscribing to system events and responding to events that require authorization.
